--- aBOUT
   Anyway... This game was released during the HUGE small little compu-
terparty  somewhere  far  from  the  rest of our world. The name of the 
party was (or actually "is" - as I'm in the  midle  of  it  right  now) 
FRUKTFEST.
   It is probably one of  the  smallest  pacman-clones  ever.  Now  I'm
talkin'in  graphical  matters,  even  though the archive's pretty small
too. It's designed for a 640x256 WB with 4 colours (but there's no  one
running on 2 colours, is there?..).

