--- pLAY
   There are some things for ya'to select in the menus during the title
sequences, such as music and gamespeed.
   The game is simple. Move that little jerky dude - yes,  he  is  VERY
small  around  with  your stick (joy ;). Collect the pacs, grab the big
pacs for some moments of immortality.  And  m o s t   important,  don't 
touch  the  ghosts  (they  are silly, and one should ALWAYS avoid silly
things (even ghosts)).

--- lEVELS
   Only  three  levels are included, but I guess you can figure out how
to make some new on your own. They are simple IFF-brushes which you may
edit in any paintpackage. Wack always starts centred in  X  and  Y.  No
more than 3 enemies may be placed on a level.

